{"tid":200952,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] [政治] [求教] 香港仲有冇救?","createTime":"2017-04-14T11:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T11:36:02.000Z","uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26b7609d012ce46d0b6018f42946f4a70001405f","tid":200952,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:37:14.000Z","msg":"眼見毓民退出政壇, 香港之前冒起嘅年輕人本土政治組織唔係慢慢冇左聲就係散左, <br />\n有d就同佢地參選理念違背,議員係立法會停留係表達訴求上,好難動搖政府,<br />\n加上777當選,中共操縱香港更加容易, 處理一啲社會議題例如教育,媒體甚至人們都三分鐘熱度,好快冇左件事,但係啲事件係真正發生緊,佢哋嘅價值並唔係只係值得幾日既重視,而係要切實既解決,但係熱潮過後又大家好似從未發生過咁, 有時候真係好無力...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n  因為切實經歷緊學運社運,更覺得好無奈, 唔知道未來嘅路應該點行落去...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心 好想改變呢個社會 可能呢個諗法好蠢 自己都未夠成熟 唔capable做到..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5080e4aff59179040b2c91e59688d5849e28362b","tid":200952,"uid":78804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26732fa2cdb163a931766cec9cc7d548213ce92a","tid":200952,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T12:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4303fb35d60342ac54dee393a4cf65005b23929b","tid":200952,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T12:08:53.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdaf50f10286aef25d4f94bf56666fc202cd66c","tid":200952,"uid":78804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca551e806c5b2bb51428c9a9574b55c6c482f340","tid":200952,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T21:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b090de6dfeda5b25fb9ec52a3668a4908c0f6fc","tid":200952,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T21:34:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d51b093e8bf75ed8672c302b7a3bb453f0f4a453","tid":200952,"uid":84354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"香港冇救架la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f0400993942133f16890b341761f58448d22df","tid":200952,"uid":14482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:17:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2a55b90e7dc274f75ccb3094c3a35c1d46720c5","tid":200952,"uid":18271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"無啦，你條柒頭仲覺得教主係好人<br />\n咁撚蠢咪學人關心社會"},{"pid":"2e082d8c08253ec532c7508f1624b0642526727f","tid":200952,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:52:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟本你地係香港先係少數<br />\n<br />\n成日話香港玩完，可以點玩完？<br />\n就算香港變到上海，深圳咁<br />\n只要仲有飯開，有西屌<br />\n<br />\n大部分人都冇所謂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇錯正如你所講生活到就得<br />\n但係其實香港人所爭取嘅 或者香港所珍貴之處係咪真係咁呢<br />\n可能我對玩完嘅定義唔同 我覺得玩完其實係指 收到中央嚴重既干預 違反咗一國兩制呢啲 甚至係佢核心價值受到蠶食 <br />\n有飯開 滿足嘅係基本嘅人權 而我地所追求既要係咪淨係局限於此？<br />\n而係我心目中呢啲values並唔係可有可無嘅事"},{"pid":"dadf83f8c9c040ce0812c3836222e879afebe578","tid":200952,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無啦，你條柒頭仲覺得教主係好人<br />\n咁撚蠢咪學人關心社會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一 點解你會覺得我認為教主係好人？<br />\n<br />\n第二 點解對於議員既去留唔屬於關心社會既一部分？<br />\n<br />\n第三 回應閣下就黃毓民觀點，若我有錯解之意，誠向你求教提出如此批判的理據，洗耳恭聽，願聞其詳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594d1ebb1fb56c6955eee827c2b87220495819d0","tid":200952,"uid":46499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:30:47.000Z","msg":"巴打曾幾何時我都覺得好灰心好冇希望 但係我相信香港仍然值得我哋去救 我哋宜家可以裝備好自己同埋影響身邊既人 如果連我哋都放棄 香港就真係冇得救 點都好 記住唔好放棄 至少仲有我與你同行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476fcad4d5a57cd331ca6c8c9be9fc856d201c91","tid":200952,"uid":106291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"要眾籌 不了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾籌有幾十萬 我仲同你沖？<br />\n<br />\n港豬真係港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}